ji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我地香港人咪香港嘅未來囉，香港嘅未來咪我地香港人嘅未來囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港唔適合香港人生活嘅時候香港人又講乜撚野未來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a9594ed667612a21d5e1270a7b7f44e3a7ec447","tid":1192890,"uid":126054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T16:13:29.000Z","msg":"學人講安全?<br />\n最唔安全就係中國法庭,DLLM<br />\n唔做已經覺得輸,要放棄; 咁點解唔死撚左佢,係人最後都要死,唔好顯世啦<br />\n就係因為以前香港人正係識返工,唔理政治,個政府先覺得自己玩哂,同個建制狗係咁出賣香港人利益,當香港人白痴<br />\n香港人咁都忍到,就一世做狗,賤過支那人"},{"pid":"cfebe748d1dd3ce5c168036396c878b724876e41","tid":1192890,"uid":49456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T16:13:53.000Z","msg":"和理非係咁解架咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8f56d3c0e2744b959716b18a64252e680b22e72","tid":1192890,"uid":55493,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T16:15:08.000Z","msg":"點同家人交代，冇父母想自己仔女變成噉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我想自己仔女生活係一個父母頂天立地嘅地方呀屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我想自己仔女唔會因為自己父母係香港人而變成弱勢社群啊屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都要同自己仔女交代架屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0a0b3cc4709a364778b6d8db8510f580032c42c","tid":1192890,"uid":235546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cfebe748d1dd3ce5c168036396c878b724876e41","tid":1192890,"uid":49456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T16:13:53.000Z","msg":"和理非係咁解架咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T16:16:03.000Z","msg":"都仲有個和平理性非暴力嘅含意喺入面嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b1e8de8f4e41b31f24d5661319ca7d25876dc9b","tid":1192890,"uid":214855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2f708f984c2c8fcc735f1bc7a5fddfed558ee92","ti